    <item>
      <title>哈里斯的副总统人选让农业问题不再成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/harris-vice-president-pick-brings-farming-issues-off-backburner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯决定选择一位农业大州的州长作为她的竞选搭档，这向萎缩的美国农业产业发出信号，该产业的首要问题可能最终会在竞选中得到一些关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/harris-vice-president-pick-brings-farming-issues-off-backburner</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺贝尔奖得主尤努斯抵达孟加拉国领导政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/nobel-winner-yunus-arrives-in-bangladesh-to-lead-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺贝尔经济学奖得主穆罕默德·尤努斯于周四抵达孟加拉国，准备举行临时政府宣誓就职仪式。在学生领导的抗议活动迫使谢赫·哈西娜逃离该国之后，尤努斯将领导临时政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/nobel-winner-yunus-arrives-in-bangladesh-to-lead-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 08:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使因“政治”冷落以色列特使将缺席长崎轰炸纪念活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/us-envoy-to-skip-nagasaki-bombing-memorial-over-political-snub-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻日本大使拉姆·伊曼纽尔将不会出席 8 月 9 日长崎原子弹爆炸纪念仪式，因为他称长崎市长不邀请以色列特使是“政治”决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/us-envoy-to-skip-nagasaki-bombing-memorial-over-political-snub-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 08:03:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加泰罗尼亚分离主义者普伊格蒙特违抗法庭判决返回西班牙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/catalan-separatist-puigdemont-defies-courts-with-return-to-spain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前加泰罗尼亚主席卡莱斯·普伊格蒙特 (Carles Puigdemont) 周四出现在巴塞罗那的一场集会上 — — 尽管他因挪用公款而被发出逮捕令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/catalan-separatist-puigdemont-defies-courts-with-return-to-spain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 07:26:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前外交官称孟加拉国可能不会这么快举行选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/bangladesh-may-not-hold-elections-so-soon-says-former-diplomat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位前高级外交官表示，孟加拉国不太可能在谢赫哈西娜被赶下台后这么快举行大选，因为看守政府可能首先进行宪法改革，以确保未来的选举不受篡改。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/bangladesh-may-not-hold-elections-so-soon-says-former-diplomat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚鲁托在抗议活动再度升温的阴影下宣誓就任内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/kenya-s-ruto-swears-in-cabinet-in-shadow-of-renewed-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托 (William Ruto) 任命了 19 名经议会批准的部长，尽管公民威胁要恢复反政府抗议活动，该抗议活动已导致数十人丧生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/kenya-s-ruto-swears-in-cabinet-in-shadow-of-renewed-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:24:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国解散政党誓言挑战保守派权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/disbanded-thai-party-members-vow-to-battle-old-guards-for-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国反对党解散后，其内部反对派成员誓言组建新组织，挑战保守派当权派的权力，这为东南亚第二大经济体的进一步政治动荡埋下了伏笔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/disbanded-thai-party-members-vow-to-battle-old-guards-for-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:01:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反种族主义抗议者为英国骚乱后带来喘息机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/anti-racism-protesters-give-uk-some-respite-after-days-of-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数千名反种族主义抗议者出现在英国各地城镇，以对抗周三晚上未能举行的极右翼示威活动，这给这个十多年来最严重的骚乱所困扰的国家带来了一丝安慰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/anti-racism-protesters-give-uk-some-respite-after-days-of-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗称以色列必须同意加沙停火以平息该地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/iran-tells-macron-israel-must-back-gaza-truce-to-ease-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统告诉法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙，美国和欧洲必须敦促以色列接受加沙停火，以缓解中东紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/iran-tells-macron-israel-must-back-gaza-truce-to-ease-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 14:42:54 GMT</pubDate>
